<ul>
	<li>Application is now a fully functional standalone app that integrates though a connector plugin with mura.</li>
	<li>New version supports Coldbox Module, Mura Plugin or Railo Extension</li>
	<li>Multi-Site support for Mura so that you can list products on different pages, and define site level settings</li>
	<li>New Account Authentication model to allow for Remote Logins like Google & Facebook in the near future.</li>
	<li>Updated Slatwall tab in the Mura admin to match Mura 6 look & feel</li>
</ul>